<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Sapchuom kingakna khat mai, Lal Isu Krista chuh;
 Lalpa thilsiem thak ahi A thu leh Thagau in,
 Van apat hung kumsuk in, A mo di'n a hung hawl,
 A thisan ngeiin a chaw'i, Sapchuomte hinna di'n.

[V2]
 2. Namtin laka teldawk te, Krista a kipum khat,
 Hukdamna khat, pienna khat, Lalpa khat, Ginna khat;
 Min khat manga limbawl in, Ankuong khat u khawmin,
 Kinepna khat mai neia, Hehpihna piek I hiu.

[V3]
 3. Gim theih leh buoina lak a nicheng galdo na ah,
 Kumsawt muonna bukim chuh thuokhat taka ngakin;
 A vangsakna bukim chuh a mita mu dingin,
 Sapchuom vangsakna lopi, Kumsawt chawlhna chang di'n.

[V4]
 4. Lei chunga a um inle, Pathien Mi-thum pumkhat,
 Lei a a tatsate cheng, Muhtheih loh a kizawm;
 Aw thiengtho leh nuomsa te, Lalpa ei vangsak in,
 Kingainiem leh nunnem a, Nang tawh kivawp zing di'n.</lyrics>
<title>THE CHURCH'S ONE FOUNDATION</title>
</song>